{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/PeriodicTimelineSchedule\/explicit(_:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"explicit"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"dates"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore24ExplicitTimelineScheduleV","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ExplicitTimelineSchedule","text":"ExplicitTimelineSchedule"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":" == "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore24ExplicitTimelineScheduleV","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ExplicitTimelineSchedule","text":"ExplicitTimelineSchedule"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":">, "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ST","text":"Sequence"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ST7ElementQa","text":"Element"},{"kind":"text","text":" == "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10Foundation4DateV","text":"Date"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The sequence of dates at which a timeline view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"updates. Use a monotonically increasing sequence of dates,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and ensure that at least one is in the future.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"dates"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Initialize a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/TimelineView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" with an explicit timeline schedule when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you want to schedule view updates at particular points in time:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let dates = [","    Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 10), \/\/ Update ten seconds from now,","    Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12) \/\/ and a few seconds later.","]","","struct MyView: View {","    var body: some View {","        TimelineView(.explicit(dates)) { context in","            Text(context.date.description)","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The timeline view updates its content on exactly the dates that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you specify, until it runs out of dates, after which it stops changing.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the dates you provide are in the past, the timeline view updates","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"exactly once with the last entry. If you only provide dates in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"future, the timeline view renders with the current date until the first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"date arrives. If you provide one or more dates in the past and one or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"more in the future, the view renders the most recent past date,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"refreshing normally on all subsequent dates.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/PeriodicTimelineSchedule"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Timeline\/TimelineSchedule.swift#L270","fileName":"TimelineSchedule.swift"},"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"explicit(_:)","modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"6.0","unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","beta":false}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore16TimelineSchedulePAAE8explicityAA08ExplicitdE0Vyqd__Gqd__AGRszSTRd__10Foundation4DateV7ElementRtd__lFZ::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore24PeriodicTimelineScheduleV","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"explicit"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ExplicitTimelineSchedule","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore24ExplicitTimelineScheduleV"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"S"},{"kind":"text","text":">"}],"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"A schedule for up